  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Top-TIP: Motion-Plan</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Top-Tip<keyword translate="true">Planning a Motion</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:520px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Tip Body" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Top-Tips: </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">To plan your motion-design</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Use the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Blend-Point-Editor" styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Segment-Editor" styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Segment Editor</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> to edit all Y-axis motion-value to be 0 - the graph plot is horizontal at zero.</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Estimate the number of segments and the timing of each segment in your motion. </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Use </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Insert-Blend-Points</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (or </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-DeleteSegment" styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Delete-Segments</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">) to split the existing segments (or remove segments) to give the total number of segments in your estimate (2)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Change Motion-Laws or leave segments as Flexible-Polynomial.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Edit the X-axis values of each Blend-Point to an approximate values</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Edit the Y-axis values of the Position graph to the approximate value.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Continue ... .</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
